snippet.title: Conquest Manager - tabletop trading cards video game
snippet.description:
Conquest Manager is a tabletop fantasy game with trading cards.
The main goal is to conquer all the creatures on the table with cards in your hand. And a little surprise after a few game play minutes awaits you, the Boss, which makes game more hard to play. Manage your deck to create a powerful strike to the enemies.

You can find us on: http://sur-games.com
itch.io platform: https://surrealism.itch.io/conquest-manager
Play on web browser here: http://sur-games.com/Unity/ConquestManager/index.html
Play on Windows, download '.exe' file: http://sur-games.com/download-conquest-manager/
